te. Please feel free to contact me with any questions. As you may know, the participation fee is calculated by dividing the Seller''s Upfront Price by the number of Participants. Please download the Request to Participate from the Documents tab, fill it out and submit it to SynPat, using this form.</p>', '<p>Thank you for your interest in aquiring a Regular License under this portfoio. In order to acquire the license, please download the Patent Licensee Agreement from the Documents tab, execute it, and submit it to SynPat using this form. SynPat will counter execute the agreement and send it back to you together with an invoice for payment of your license fees, which will be 50% higher than the price each Participant paid.</p>\n<p>In the event that your license was already acquired (as a Strategic License) by another operating company, SynPat will inform you about that and will not be able to sell the license to you.</p>', '<p>Thank you for your interest in aquiring a Validated License under this patent portfoio. We call it a Validated License because so many other licensees have validated this patent portfolio since it was introduced by SynPat. In order to acquire the license, please download the Patent License Agreement from the Documents tab, execute it, and upload it using the button below. SynPat will counter execute the agreement and send it back to you together with an invoice for payment of your license fees, which will be 100% higher than the amount each Regular Licensee paid.</p>\n<p>In the event that your license was already acquired by another operating company, SynPat will inform you about that and will not be able to sell the license to you.</p>', 0, NULL, '12345', '', 'admin@123', '', '12345', NULL, '', '12345', NULL, '12345', '12345', '', '12345', '', '12345', '', 'admin@123');
